ast Hanover, NJ.[5] "Product Information. Zortress (everolimus)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[6] "Product Information. Afinitor (everolimus)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.', 1767365204);
